sentences.english: Currently Sharp does not make compressors, a key air conditioner component.

sentences.english: Oil-free compressors of course, are the logical choice for instrument-air supplies.

sentences.english: The invention simultaneously provides an internal-combustion engine and a compressor using the movable shaft.
sentences.chinese: 本發明同時提供使用上述動軸的內燃機和壓縮機。

sentences.english: Our company are provide screw type compressor of overhaul service.

sentences.english: When it rains, a traditional compressor kicks in to cut moisture.

sentences.english: Used as the heater for compressors of refrigerators, freezers and air conditioners.

sentences.english: Bock compressors are manufactured on the latest generation of production and assembly plant.

sentences.english: The article deals with certain measures taken for surge and anti - surge control of centrifugal compressor.

sentences.english: Take compressor's intercooler for example, main reasons of failure is analyzed.

sentences.english: Drying machine and the capacity of filter should be consistent with the displacement compressors.

sentences.english: The center line of condenser shall be opposite to the exhaust end of syn gas compressor turbine.

sentences.english: We are Level agents for Copeland compressor in China.

sentences.english: The air compressor has been repaired and fitted back in place.

sentences.english: Grounding tie-in shall be provided for compressor units.

sentences.english: Inside the cabinet are an air compressor and a vacuum pump.
